            "tag": "P",
            "text": "Margate City is a premier Jersey Shore destination, offering a relaxed coastal lifestyle with an upscale twist. Known for its pristine beaches, lively restaurant scene, and walkable streets, Margate is a favorite for retirees, second-home buyers, and families who want a blend of small-town charm and seasonal vibrancy. Housing includes everything from charming bungalows and modern condos to luxurious waterfront estates. Margate’s strong community feel, paired with its convenient location just south of Atlantic City, makes it one of the most desirable places to live along the coast.",
