            "text": "Somers Point is a vibrant bayside city known for its marinas, dining scene, and classic South Jersey shore lifestyle. Located just before the Ocean City bridge, it’s a prime location for boaters, commuters, and beach lovers alike. Housing options include waterfront condos, cozy bungalows, and larger single-family homes, many with bay or marina views. With its walkable bayfront, summer concerts, and strong year-round community, Somers Point appeals to retirees, second-home buyers, and families who want convenience, charm, and access to both the shore and inland amenities.",
