            "text": "Medford Lakes Borough is a unique community best known for its rustic log cabin homes and network of scenic lakes. The borough offers a resort-like lifestyle with opportunities for swimming, boating, and fishing right in the neighborhood. Housing is dominated by single-family homes, many with waterfront access or wooded lots, creating a distinctive character unlike anywhere else in South Jersey. Despite its tucked-away setting, Medford Lakes is close to Route 70, making it convenient for commuters and those looking to balance natural beauty with accessibility.",
