            "text": "Cherry Hill is one of Camden County’s most sought-after communities, known for its excellent schools, convenient shopping, and family-friendly neighborhoods. Located just minutes from Philadelphia, it offers an easy commute via Route 70, I-295, or the nearby PATCO line. Homebuyers are drawn to the wide variety of housing options—from mid-century ranchers to modern townhomes and spacious single-family homes.",
