            "tag": "P",
            "text": "The township boasts major retail hubs like the Cherry Hill Mall, as well as countless restaurants, parks, and cultural attractions. Families appreciate the highly rated Cherry Hill Public Schools, while outdoor lovers enjoy spots like Croft Farm and Cooper River Park. Whether you’re a first-time buyer or upgrading to a forever home, Cherry Hill combines suburban comfort with urban convenience.",
