            "text": "Gloucester Township is one of Camden County’s largest and most diverse communities, offering a wide range of neighborhoods, home styles, and amenities. With sections like Blackwood, Sicklerville, and Erial, the township has something for every buyer—from first-timers to growing families looking for more space.",
