            "text": "The area features newer developments, townhome communities, and established neighborhoods with tree-lined streets. It’s known for its highly rated schools in the Black Horse Pike Regional School District and easy access to Route 42, the Atlantic City Expressway, and NJ Transit’s Avandale and Lindenwold stations. Shoppers enjoy the Gloucester Premium Outlets and plenty of local retail and dining.",
