            "text": "The real estate here includes everything from beautifully preserved Victorians to updated single-family homes, often with generous front porches and well-kept yards. The Haddon Heights School District is well-regarded, and residents enjoy easy access to the PATCO Speedline, Route 295, and nearby towns like Haddonfield and Audubon.",
