            "text": "Magnolia is a small borough with a welcoming, hometown feel. It’s a great option for buyers seeking an affordable and convenient place to live in Camden County. With a mix of well-kept single-family homes and charming streetscapes, Magnolia offers quiet living without straying far from major roadways or shopping hubs. It is also home to one of the only remaining original single-arch McDonald’s restaurants.",
