            "text": "The borough is served by the Magnolia School District, and residents enjoy local parks, playgrounds, and community events throughout the year. Its central location near the White Horse Pike, I-295, and the PATCO line makes commuting a breeze. Whether you’re heading to Philly or down the Shore, you’re well-connected.",
