            "text": "Mount Ephraim is a friendly borough that offers a great mix of small-town charm and commuter convenience. Nestled between Bellmawr and Haddon Heights, it’s a great option for buyers seeking an affordable, suburban community with easy access to Philadelphia and nearby Camden County towns.",
