            "text": "The housing stock includes Cape Cods, ranchers, and traditional single-family homes on quiet, well-kept streets. Residents appreciate the walkability of the town, its local parks, and the close-knit community feel. Route 130, I-76, and I-295 are all nearby, making it a breeze to get wherever you need to go.",
            "href": "",
            "type": "",
            "placeholder": ""
