            "text": "The borough’s small downtown includes coffee shops, pubs, and local favorites, while Newton Lake Park offers beautiful views and outdoor recreation. Oaklyn is part of the Collingswood School District and enjoys close proximity to the PATCO line, making it a solid choice for Philly commuters.",
