            "text": "West Cape May is a charming, historic community located just west of Cape May City. Known for its Victorian cottages, small farms, and vibrant local culture, it offers buyers a blend of historic character and modern convenience. The town has a reputation for community pride, hosting popular events like farmers markets and seasonal festivals. With walkable streets, proximity to Cape May’s shopping and dining, and easy access to the beach, West Cape May appeals to buyers seeking a quieter lifestyle while still enjoying the amenities of a premier shore destination.",
