            "text": "Wildwood Crest offers a quieter, more relaxed atmosphere than its neighbor Wildwood, while still providing wide beaches and strong seasonal appeal. Known for its family-friendly vibe, clean streets, and well-kept public spaces, the Crest attracts buyers looking for resort-style living without the noise of the boardwalk. The real estate market includes everything from beachfront condos to upscale single-family homes, many with ocean views. Strong demand for second homes and rentals makes Wildwood Crest a popular investment destination as well.",
