            "text": "Vineland is the largest city in Cumberland County and serves as a regional hub for shopping, dining, and employment. Known for its diverse neighborhoods and convenient location along Route 55, Vineland offers a wide range of housing options—from affordable starter homes to newer subdivisions and larger properties on the outskirts. The city has a strong sense of community, supported by local festivals, recreational programs, and cultural venues. With abundant parks, retail centers, and easy access to both Philadelphia and the Jersey Shore, Vineland appeals to families, commuters, and anyone seeking a balance of city amenities with South Jersey affordability.",
