            "text": "Woodstown is one of Salem County’s most charming towns, offering a blend of historic appeal and modern convenience. Known for its beautiful Victorian homes, tree-lined streets, and vibrant small-town atmosphere, Woodstown is ideal for buyers seeking a close-knit community with character. The town boasts a walkable downtown with local shops, restaurants, and cafes, as well as highly rated schools. With easy access to Route 40 and Route 45, residents enjoy a manageable commute to larger cities while benefiting from the peaceful surroundings. From family-friendly neighborhoods to homes with historic flair, Woodstown offers a diverse range of properties. Community events, farmers markets, and seasonal parades make it an engaging place to live year-round. For homebuyers looking for a welcoming town that balances tradition and comfort, Woodstown is a standout choice in Salem County.",
