            "text": "New Jersey Compact (8,723 sq. miles), New Jersey balances urban North Jersey (e.g., Newark, Jersey City) tied to NYC with suburban/rural South Jersey (e.g., Cape May, Atlantic City) connected to Philadelphia. Its location between two major cities makes it both a commuter and cultural hub.",
            "href": "",
